- true: Enabled.
- false: Disabled.', example='false'),
  enableKibanaPublicNetwork?: boolean(name='enableKibanaPublicNetwork', description='Indicates whether public network access to Kibana is enabled. Valid values:

- true: Enabled.
- false: Disabled.', example='true'),
