- true: Enabled.
- false: Disabled.', example='true'),
  endTime?: long(name='endTime', description='The time when the instance expires. For pay-as-you-go instances, the default value is 100 years.', example='5'),
  esConfig?: map[string]string(name='esConfig', description='The YML file configuration of the instance.'),
  esIPWhitelist?: [ string ](name='esIPWhitelist', description='The private network access whitelist configuration of the instance (deprecated).'),
  esVersion?: string(name='esVersion', description='The instance version.', example='6.3.2_with_X-Pack'),
  extendConfigs?: [  map[string]any ](name='extendConfigs', description='The extension parameter settings of the instance.'),
